          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 5374,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The following examples represent widely used marketing measures in the railway sector's online retail, from which customers benefit in the form of lower prices or convenience:",
