          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 8018,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Automatic renewals of discount cards or subscriptions for tickets for certain routes, in case the customer is adequately informed about the renewal in accordance with relevant consumer protection regulation. This practice offers convenience to regular users and is a standard business model for subscription services, provided clear and compliant consumer information is supplied.",
        "chunk_meta": {
