        "text": "In order to facilitate and speed up the process of purchasing e-tickets, rail carriers collect, analyze, and use passenger data, including travel frequency, most frequently chosen train class and category, preferred times, and destinations. The processing of such data facilitates and speeds up the purchase process, for example by auto-filling of some boxes or repurchase for another date.",
