          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 10439,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "We urge the Commission, as it proceeds with the Impact Assessment, to ensure that the scope of the Digital Fairness Act is precisely defined to target genuinely deceptive or manipulative practices, without hindering beneficial and transparent commercial practices essential to the functioning of the digital single market. We trust that the Digital Fairness Act will support the Commission’s objective of increasing the EU’s competitiveness, which includes a focus on simplification and measures to remove barriers in the Single Market.",
